Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_grxstsph

Receive Status Read and Pop Register, Host Mode (GRXSTSPH)

A read to the Receive Status Read and Pop register returns and additionally pops the top data entry out of the RxFIFO. This Description is only valid when the core is in Host Mode. For Device Mode use USBC_GRXSTSPD instead. NOTE: GRXSTSPH and GRXSTSPD are physically the same register and share the same offset in the O2P USB core. The offset difference shown in this document is for software clarity and is actually ignored by the hardware.
